---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base title="Terms of Service" description="Terms and conditions for using vkrama">
  <div class="container-page max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-surface-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-surface max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">By accessing or using vkrama.com.np, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">2. Account Registration</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-surface-600 space-y-1">
          <li>You must provide accurate and complete information when creating an account</li>
          <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials</li>
          <li>You must be at least 18 years old to create an account</li>
          <li>One account per person; duplicate accounts may be removed</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">3. Orders and Payments</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-surface-600 space-y-1">
          <li>All orders are subject to product availability</li>
          <li>Prices are in Nepalese Rupees (NPR) and include applicable taxes unless stated otherwise</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to cancel orders due to pricing errors or stock limitations</li>
          <li>Payment must be completed before order processing</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">4. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-surface-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Delivery times are estimates and may vary</li>
          <li>Risk of loss transfers to you upon delivery</li>
          <li>Inspect packages upon arrival and report damages within 48 hours</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">5. Returns and Refunds</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">Items may be returned within 7 days of delivery if they are unused, undamaged, and in original packaging. Perishable and personalized items are non-returnable. Refunds are processed to the original payment method within 5-7 business days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">6. Product Descriptions</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">We strive for accuracy in product descriptions and images. However, colors may appear differently on your screen. We are not liable for minor variations.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">7. Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-surface-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Using the site for illegal purposes</li>
          <li>Attempting to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
          <li>Interfering with the site's functionality</li>
          <li>Posting fraudulent reviews or misleading content</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">To the maximum extent permitted by law, vkrama shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of updated terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-surface-900 mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@vkrama.com.np" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700">support@vkrama.com.np</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
